ROMANIAN EMBASSY IN BEIJING BACKS NATIONAL FRONT+

     BEIJING, DEC. 24 KYODO - THE ROMANIAN EMBASSY IN BEIJING HAS
DECLARED ITS BACKING FOR THE NATIONAL SALVATION FRONT COUNCIL WHICH
CAPTURED POWER AFTER THE GOVERNMENT OF PRESIDENT NICOLAE CEAUSESCU
WAS OVERTHROWN TWO DAYS AGO.
     A MINISTER AT THE EMBASSY CALLED ON THE OFFICIAL CHINESE XINHUA
NEWS AGENCY TO REPORT THE EMBASSY'S DECLARATION OF SUPPORT FOR THE
COUNCIL.
     THE MINISTER SAID HE WILL INFORM THE CHINESE FOREIGN MINISTRY
OF THE EMBASSY'S BACKING FOR THE NEW REGIME.



