powerful execution' that he has been campaigning for.  Many of those
who voted for him must think the same way,'' the Yomiuri said.
     On Wednesday, Ozawa scored an overwhelming victory over his
long-time political ally, former Prime Minister Tsutomu Hata, to
become the head of Shishinto.



