Liberal Democratic Party (LDP), LDP premiers made it a rule to pay a
New Year visit to Ise.
     Ise Shrine enshrines the goddess Amaterasu, the legendary
ancestor of the imperial family, while Yasukuni Shrine enshrines the
Japanese military war dead.
     Murayama, who came to power in June last year, did not go to Ise
in January this year because of a cold.



