REED INTERNATIONAL REPORTS SIX MONTH FIGURES

Reed International (London) reports that sales for the six
month period ending September 30 increased 5.8% to L764.1
million. Operating profit for the period increased 7.3%,
going to L119.7 million. Sales in the U.S. rose 8% to L155
million while operating profit decreased 3% to L27 million.





